<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_8488" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Staatsrat Tessin an Alfred Escher, Bellinzona, Dienstag, 16. April 1872</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>BAR</institution><idno type="original">CH-BAR#J1.81#1000/1377#5*</idno><idno>J I.81</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Gotthardbahn-Gesellschaft (GB)</term><term>Regierungsrat TI</term><term>Grosser Rat TI</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><orgName type="addressee">Staatsrat Tessin</orgName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Bellinzona</placeName><date when="1872-04-16">16. April 1872</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B7239"/><ref type="next" target="B2611"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B2611"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B7239"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      <div type="annotation"><p rend="left" xml:id="K_8488_p1"><lb xml:id="p1-l1"/><hi rend="printed"><choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice></hi> 15264.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="dateline"><p rend="right" xml:id="K_8488_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l2"/><hi rend="printed"><placeName key="Bellinzona">Bellinzona</placeName>,</hi> il <date when="1872-04-16">16. Aprile <hi rend="printed">187</hi>2</date> </p></div>
      <p rend="center" xml:id="K_8488_p3"><hi rend="printed">
          <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>CONFEDERAZIONE SVIZZERA <note type="com" xml:id="K_8488_c1">Auf der ersten Briefseite ist das Wappen des Kantons
              <placeName key="Tessin">Tessin</placeName> abgebildet.</note> <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>IL CONSIGLIO DI STATO 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>del Cantone del <placeName key="Tessin">Ticino</placeName> </hi></p>
      
      <div type="opener"><p rend="center" xml:id="K_8488_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>al
        <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/><hi><choice><abbr>Sig<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr><expan>Signore (Herr)</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Dott.</abbr><expan>Dottore (Doktor)</expan></choice> Alfredo Escher</hi>
      <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>Consigliere nazionale
      <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Presidente della Direzione della Ferrovia del Gottardo
      <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/><hi rend="underline"><placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurigo</placeName></hi></p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_8488_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>Onoratissimo Signore</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_8488_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>Abbiamo l'onore e la soddisfazione di trasmetterle il Decreto
        <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/><date when="1872-04-15">15 corrente mese</date> col quale il Gran Consiglio, sulla
        <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>nostra iniziativa, ha conferito alla <choice><abbr>S. V.</abbr><expan>Signoria Vostra (Eure Herrschaft)</expan></choice>, ad
        <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>unanimità di voti, la Cittadinanza <placeName key="Tessin">Ticinese</placeName>.</p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_8488_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>Speriamo che <choice><abbr>S. V.</abbr><expan>Signoria Vostra (Eure Herrschaft)</expan></choice> vorrà aggradire questa dimostrazione di
        <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>alta stima e riconoscenza, che suolsi dalle nostre
        <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>Autorità accordare nelle occassioni solenni a
        <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>personaggi illustri, i quali abbiano prestato
        <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>eminenti servigi nazionali, come è avvenuto nel
        <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>1815 verso il <hi>Generale <persName key="La Harpe Frédéric-César de">La Harpe</persName></hi>, e nel
        <pb n="2"/><lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>1848 verso il <hi>Generale <persName key="Dufour Guillaume-Henri">Dufour</persName></hi>.</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer"><p rend="left" xml:id="K_8488_p8"><lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>Con ciò la preghiamo di accogliere eziandio i
        <lb xml:id="p2-l3"/>sensi della nostra distintissima considerazione.</p> </div>
      <div type="signature"><p rend="center" xml:id="K_8488_p9"><lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>Per il Consiglio di Stato
        <lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>Il Presidente
        <lb xml:id="p2-l6"/><persName key="Forni Carlo Antonio">C. A. Forni</persName>
      </p>
      <p rend="right" xml:id="K_8488_p10"><lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>Il <choice><abbr>Consigl<hi rend="sup">e</hi> Segret<hi rend="sup">o</hi> di Stato</abbr><expan>Consigliere Segretario di Stato (Staatsratssekretär)</expan></choice>
        <lb xml:id="p2-l8"/><persName key="Patocchi Michele">M. Patocchi<!-- 24.05.2015, VP: Transkription angepasst --></persName> </p></div>
    </back></text></TEI>